<section class="impact">
  <div class="container impact-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="impact-title">Más que un punto de venta.<br/>Tu sistema operativo de negocio.</h2>
      <p class="impact-desc">SACS conecta ventas, inventario, clientes y reportes en un solo ecosistema inteligente.</p>
      <div class="impact-ctas">
        <a class="btn-impact btn-impact-white" href="/contacto">Empieza gratis</a>
        <a class="btn-impact btn-impact-outline" href="/producto">Explorar producto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .impact {
    background: #1A1A2E;
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .impact {
      padding: var(--space-32) 0;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .impact {
      padding: var(--space-40) 0;
    }
  }

  .impact-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .impact-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .impact-desc {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .impact-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-impact {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .btn-impact:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-impact-white {
    background: #fff;
    color: #0f0f1a;
  }

  .btn-impact-white:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .btn-impact-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-impact-outline:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  /* ─── Reduced motion ─── */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .btn-impact-white:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
